# ─── Google Drive Sync ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for the "Connect Google Drive" sync feature in Settings.
#
# How to get a free Client ID (takes ~5 minutes):
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   2. Create a project (or pick an existing one)
#   3. APIs & Services → Enable APIs → enable "Google Drive API"
#   4. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create Credential → OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#      • Application type: Web application
#      • Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173  (add your prod URL too)
#   5. Copy the Client ID below
#   6. APIs & Services → OAuth consent screen → add your email as a Test User
#      (until you publish the app, only test users can sign in)
#
# Cost: completely free. Uses the user's own Google Drive quota (15 GB free).
#
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID.apps.googleusercontent.com
